skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: beer selector
des:
Ever get tired of one beer and don't know what beer you want to try or buy next? Well I do. This skill will select a random beer type from the list and suggest it to you! Theres even a surprise suggestion in there too! ;)

Next time before going out to buy beer, enable this app and get the beer it suggests!

*Icon made by Madebyoliver from flaticon
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
